  <title>Gio.Drive::poll_for_media</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function vfunc_poll_for_media(cancellable: Gio.Cancellable, callback: Gio.AsyncReadyCallback): void {
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Asynchronously polls <code>drive</code> to see if media has been inserted or removed.</p>  <p>When the operation is finished, <code>callback</code> will be called.
You can then call <link xref="Gio.Drive.poll_for_media_finish"/> to obtain the
result of the operation.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>cancellable</code></title>
  <p>optional <link xref="Gio.Cancellable"/> object, <code>null</code> to ignore.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>callback</code></title>
  <p>a <link xref="Gio.AsyncReadyCallback"/>, or <code>null</code>.</p>
</item>
</terms>

